}
```

Explanation:

- `background-color` with an rgba value provides the color transparency. The button will be 70% opaque with the primary color.
- The `border-radius` gives it a rounded, modern feel.
- The `transition` will make sure any hover effect or color change appears smooth to the eye.
- The `:hover` pseudo-class darkens the button slightly and lifts it up (`translateY`) to give feedback to the user.
- The `:active` pseudo-class resets the lift effect, simulating a button press.

