To integrate this with the JavaScript theme switcher:

1. Place a `data-theme` attribute on the `<body>` or a parent container. The JavaScript function will toggle this attribute based on user choice.
2. Modify the `changeTheme` function to set the `data-theme` attribute:

```javascript
function changeTheme(theme) {
    document.body.setAttribute('data-theme', theme);
}
```

