        margin: 10px 0;
    }

    .container {
        width: 95%;
    }
}
```

This CSS setup includes a responsive design, ensuring the website looks good on both desktop and mobile devices. The primary and secondary colors are applied to the header and footer, creating a cohesive look that aligns with the brand's color scheme.

