### Base CSS for Colorful Socks Website

```css
/* Base CSS for Colorful Socks Website */

:root {
    --primary-color: #e63946; /* Bright red */
    --secondary-color: #f1faee; /* Light cream */
    --accent-color: #a8dadc; /* Soft teal */
    --text-color: #1d3557; /* Dark blue */
}

body {
    font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background-color: var(--secondary-color);
    color: var(--text-color);
}

h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
    font-family: 'Helvetica', sans-serif;
    color: var(--primary-color);
}

a {
    color: var(--primary-color);
    text-decoration: none;
}

a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
}

.navbar {
    background-color: var(--secondary-color);
    padding: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
}

.nav-links {
    list-style-type: none;
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
}

.hero-content {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background-color: var(--accent-color);
}

section {
    padding: 2rem 0;
}

footer {
    background-color: var(--primary-color);
    color: var(--secondary-color);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1rem 0;
}

/* AOS Animation Overrides */
[data-aos] {
    transition-property: transform, opacity;
}

```

This CSS sets up the basic styling for the website, including color variables, font families, and some basic layout for the header, hero section, and footer. The colors are vibrant and align with the brand's theme, while the layout is kept simple and clean.

